quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  53,45,"wanh khalaq alzwjyn: aldhikr walantha min al'iinsan walhywan, min nutfat tusabb fi alrhm"
  53,46,"wanh khalaq alzwjyn: aldhikr walantha min al'iinsan walhywan, min nutfat tusabb fi alrhm"
  53,47,"wan ealaa rabik -ayha alrswl- 'iieadat khalaqahum baed mmathm, wahi alnash'at al'ukhraa yawm alqyamt"
  53,48,"wanh hu aghna man sha' min khalaqah balmal, wmllakh lahum wardahm bh"
  53,49,"wanh subhanah wteala hu rabu alshshiera, wahu najam mdy', kan bed 'ahl aljahiliat yebdwnh min dun allh"
  53,50,"wanh subhanah wteala 'ahlak eadana alawla, wahum qawm hwd, wa'ahlak thmwd, wahum qawm salh, falam yubq minhum ahdana, wa'ahlak qawm nuh qblu. hwla' kanuu 'ashada tmrdana wa'aezam kfrana min aladhin jawu min bedhm. wmdayn qawm lut qalbiha allah elyhm, wajaeal ealiaha saflha, falbsha ma albsha min alhjart"
  53,51,"wanh subhanah wteala 'ahlak eadana alawla, wahum qawm hwd, wa'ahlak thmwd, wahum qawm salh, falam yubq minhum ahdana, wa'ahlak qawm nuh qblu. hwla' kanuu 'ashada tmrdana wa'aezam kfrana min aladhin jawu min bedhm. wmdayn qawm lut qalbiha allah elyhm, wajaeal ealiaha saflha, falbsha ma albsha min alhjart"
  53,52,"wanh subhanah wteala 'ahlak eadana alawla, wahum qawm hwd, wa'ahlak thmwd, wahum qawm salh, falam yubq minhum ahdana, wa'ahlak qawm nuh qblu. hwla' kanuu 'ashada tmrdana wa'aezam kfrana min aladhin jawu min bedhm. wmdayn qawm lut qalbiha allah elyhm, wajaeal ealiaha saflha, falbsha ma albsha min alhjart"
  53,53,"wa'anah subhanah wteala 'ahlak eadana alawla, wahum qawm hwd, wa'ahlak thmwd, wahum qawm salh, falam yubq minhum ahdana, wa'ahlak qawm nuh qblu. hwla' kanuu 'ashada tmrdana wa'aezam kfrana min aladhin jawu min bedhm. wmdayn qawm lut qalbiha allah elyhm, wajaeal ealiaha saflha, falbsha ma albsha min alhjart"
  53,54,"wanh subhanah wteala 'ahlak eadana alawla, wahum qawm hwd, wa'ahlak thmwd, wahum qawm salh, falam yubq minhum ahdana, wa'ahlak qawm nuh qblu. hwla' kanuu 'ashada tmrdana wa'aezam kfrana min aladhin jawu min bedhm. wmdayn qawm lut qalbiha allah elyhm, wajaeal ealiaha saflha, falbsha ma albsha min alhjart"
  53,55,fbay nem rabik elyk- 'ayuha al'iinsan almkdhb- tashuk?
  53,56,"hdha muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, nadhir bialhaqi aldhy 'andhir bih al'anbia' qblh, falays bbde min alrsl"
  53,57,"qrbt alqiamat wdna wqtha, la ydfeha 'idhana min dun allah ahd, wala yattalie ealaa waqt wqweha 'iilaa allh"
  53,58,"qrbt alqiamat wdna wqtha, la ydfeha 'idhana min dun allah ahd, wala yattalie ealaa waqt wqweha 'iilaa allh"
  53,59,"afmin hdha alquran taejabun -ayha almshrkwn- min 'an yakun shyhana, watadhakun minh sukhriat wasthza'an, wala tabkun khwfana min weydh, wa'antum lahwn mueridun enh? fasjuduu lilah wa'akhlasuu alebadt lah whdh, wsllimu lah amwrkm"
  53,60,"afmin hdha alquran taejabun -ayha almshrkwn- min 'an yakun shyhana, watadhakun minh sukhriat wasthza'an, wala tabkun khwfana min weydh, wa'antum lahwn mueridun enh? fasjuduu lilah wa'akhlasuu alebadt lah whdh, wsllimu lah amwrkm"
  53,61,"afmin hdha alquran taejabun -ayha almshrkwn- min 'an yakun shyhana, watadhakun minh sukhriat wasthza'an, wala tabkun khwfana min weydh, wa'antum lahwn mueridun enh? fasjuduu lilah wa'akhlasuu alebadt lah whdh, wsllimu lah amwrkm"
  53,62,"afmin hdha alquran taejabun -ayha almshrkwn- min 'an yakun shyhana, watadhakun minh sukhriat wasthza'an, wala tabkun khwfana min weydh, wa'antum lahwn mueridun enh? fasjuduu lilah wa'akhlasuu alebadt lah whdh, wsllimu lah amwrkm"
  54,1,"dnt alqyamt, wanflq alqamar flqtyn, hin sa'al kafaar \"mk\" alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wasalam 'ana yurihim ayt, fadaea allh, farahm tilk alayt"
  54,2,"w'in yar almushrikun dalilana wbrhanana ealaa sidq alrasul muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, yuerdu ean al'iiman bih wtsdyqh mukadhibin mnkryn, wyqwlu baed zuhur aldlyl: hdha sihr batl dhahib mdmhl la dwam lh"
  54,3,"wkdhdhabu alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm, watabaeuu dalalatihim wama dethm 'iilayh ahwawhm min altkdhyb, wkll 'amr min khayr 'aw sharun waqie bi'ahlih yawm alqiamat eind zuhur althawab waleqab"
  54,4,"wlqd ja' kafaar quraysh min 'anba' al'umam almkdhbt brslha, wama hll biha min aledhab, ma fih kifayat lrdehm ean kufruhum wdlalhm"
  54,5,"hdha alquran aldhy ja'ahum hikmat ezymt balighat ghaytha, fa'aya shay' tughni alnudhur ean qawm 'aeraduu wkdhdhabu bha?"
  54,6,"faerd -ayha alrswl- enhm, wantazir bihim ywmana ezymana. yawm yadeu almalik bnfkhh fi \"alqrn\" 'iilaa 'amr fzye mnkr, wahu mawqif alhsab"